			<p>I love Snowball Cookies!  My Mama would make these amazing, powdered sugar balls of love every Christmas&#8230;.those cookies meant love and yummy to me.  I remember coming home for the holidays and she would have a batch of these waiting for me with a large glass of milk.</p>
<p>I lost my Mama to cancer in 2007&#8230;.but through her recipes and these yummy cookies, she is always around me in the kitchen.</p>
<p>Thanks for sharing this recipe&#8230;.you&#8217;ve made me smile today.</p>
