		<div class="comment-content">
						
			<p>These cookies are delightful!  The only thing I changed was the glaze.  I tried using organic powdered sugar, but this yielded a glaze with an unappealing shade of gray.  So, I switched to a chocolate glaze made with melted chocolate chips.  This worked great and looked lovely with the crushed candy canes on top.  Thank you so much.</p>
		</div><!-- end .comment-content -->

